Package org.odpi.openmetadata.viewservices.dino.server.spring

Class DinoViewRESTResource

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.viewservices.dino.server.spring.DinoViewRESTResource
@RestController @RequestMapping("/servers/{viewServerName}/open-metadata/view-services/dino/users/{userId}") public class DinoViewRESTResource extends Object
The DinoViewRESTResource provides the Spring API endpoints of the Dino Open Metadata View Service (OMVS). This interface provides an interfaces for Egeria operators.
